           EVALUATE  SQLCODE
               WHEN  CO-OK
      *（업종코드）대분류 기타->금융업으로 변경
                     IF  RJL0015-LAG-CLSFI-BZTYP-CD = CO-CHA-000 OR
                         RJL0015-LAG-CLSFI-BZTYP-CD = SPACE      OR
                         RJL0015-LAG-CLSFI-BZTYP-CD(1:1) = SPACE
                         MOVE  CO-CHA-C25
                           TO  RJL0015-LAG-CLSFI-BZTYP-CD
                     END-IF
               WHEN  CO-NOT-FOUND
      *（업종코드）대분류 기타->금융업으로 변경
      *              업종코드
                     MOVE  CO-CHA-C25
                       TO  RJL0015-LAG-CLSFI-BZTYP-CD
               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'KJL0015'     TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                     MOVE 'SELECT'      TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                     MOVE  SQLCODE      TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
